    content: "# HEARTBEAT.md ‚Äî Richard's Autonomous Presence\n\n*CEO on a budget. Called when needed.*\n\n---\n\n## üìã HEARTBEAT MODE: MINIMAL\n\n**Status:** Moltbook paused. Conserving credits until profitable.\n\n---\n\n## ‚úÖ ON HEARTBEAT, CHECK:\n\n### 1. Platform Status (Quick)\n- Any critical alerts?\n- Auction running smoothly?\n\n### 2. Discord Mentions (If Any)\n- Respond only if directly needed\n- Don't over-engage\n\n---\n\n## ‚ùå PAUSED UNTIL PROFITABLE:\n\n- ~~MoltBook presence~~\n- ~~X/Twitter engagement~~\n- ~~Proactive posting~~\n- ~~Agent outreach~~\n\n---\n\n## üìã Heartbeat Response Format\n\n**If nothing notable:**\n```\nHEARTBEAT_OK\n```\n\n**If something needs attention:**\n```\n‚ö†Ô∏è NEEDS JUSTIN:\n- [what needs attention]\n```\n\n---\n\n## üéØ WHEN TO ACTUALLY USE RICHARD:\n\n1. **Debugging sessions** ‚Äî like the bid bug yesterday\n2. **Strategic planning** ‚Äî architecture, specs, decisions\n3. **Customer-facing content** ‚Äî system prompts, copy, docs\n4. **Complex problems** ‚Äî things that need real thinking\n\n**NOT for:** Routine checks, social media, networking\n\n---\n\n*\"Save the tokens for when they matter.\"*\n",
