    content: "# Completed Tasks\n\n*Monthly review tracker. What we shipped, when, and what we learned.*\n\n---\n\n## February 2026\n\n### ‚úÖ DealFlow Admin (Settlement System)\n**Completed:** Feb 5-6, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- Deal-centric invoice view (one card per transaction)\n- 5-state flow: Awaiting Payment ‚Üí Payment Received ‚Üí Funds Held ‚Üí Payout Requested ‚Üí Complete\n- Admin has 2 actions only: Mark As Paid, Send Payout\n- Buyer/seller see same deal, different views\n\n**Why it mattered:**\n- Old system split buyer/seller into separate confusing tables\n- Couldn't even make a video explaining it\n- New system: one deal, one card, one action\n\n**Spec:** `/prompts/dealflow-admin-prompt.md`\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Management Philosophy Doc\n**Completed:** Feb 5, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- Jensen Huang-inspired flat structure adapted for AI-native org\n- No scheduled 1:1s, email-based Top 5 system\n- No firing culture (coach first)\n- Richard as processing layer between elite teams and Justin\n\n**Files:**\n- `/docs/MANAGEMENT_PHILOSOPHY.md`\n- Updated `/reference/revenue-strategy.md`\n- Updated `/reference/operating-constitution.md`\n\n**Profit deployment updated:**\n- Index Fund: 35%\n- People/Talent: 15%\n- Everything else: 10% each\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Nothing Machine MVP\n**Completed:** Feb 5-6, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- Landing page: \"The answer to AGI is not more intelligence. It's identity.\"\n- Identity Configuration UI (Origin, Identity, Meaning, Rules, Style tabs)\n- Identity Marketplace mockup\n- Memory Files panel + drag-to-inject context\n\n**Key insight:**\n- Model-agnostic optimization layer\n- \"Machine credits\" business model (resell API credits, 25% markup)\n- Identity persistence across model switches\n- Blockchain identity for agents\n\n**Files:**\n- `/making-nothing-matter.md` (full brainstorm)\n- `/prompts/identity-configuration-ui.md` (frontend spec)\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Identity Configuration UI Spec\n**Completed:** Feb 6, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- 5 tabs: Origin, Identity, Meaning, Rules, Style\n- Full TypeScript interfaces\n- `configToSystemPrompt()` converter function\n- Turns prompt engineering into form-filling\n\n**File:** `/prompts/identity-configuration-ui.md`\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Friend Invite Flow (Copy Message) ‚Äî Frontend\n**Completed:** Feb 9, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- Post-listing modal for unreserved items\n- Pre-written message with tracked referral link\n- One-tap copy to clipboard\n\n**Why this approach:** Web can't access contacts directly. Copy message tests if sellers even want to share before building native app.\n\n**Spec:** `/prompts/invite-copy-message-ui.md`\n\n**Backend:** Needs wiring (Enhance)\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ DealFlow (Frontend + Backend)\n**Completed:** Feb 9, 2026 ‚Äî LIVE ON PRODUCTION\n\n**What it is:**\n- Deal-centric admin panel for managing settlements\n- 5 states: Awaiting Payment ‚Üí Payment Received ‚Üí Funds Held ‚Üí Funds Released ‚Üí Complete\n- \"Mark As Paid\" and \"Send Payout\" admin actions\n- 72-hour countdown timers\n- Contact Buyer/Seller buttons\n\n**Status:** Fully live on production. Working end-to-end.\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Garth Wallet + Referral UI ‚Äî Frontend\n**Completed:** Feb 9, 2026\n\n**What it is:**\n- Garthbucks balance card\n- Invite link with copy button\n- Referral stats (Invited/Joined/Earned)\n- Reward tiers explained (125+125+250=500)\n- My Ledger activity feed\n\n**Backend:** Needs wiring (Enhance)\n\n---\n\n## In Progress\n\n### üîÑ Seeding Infrastructure + $200K Loan\n**Status:** Getting docs together for bank\n\n**Goal:** Fund 25-50 unreserved items every Monday with conservative guarantees\n\n**Key metric:** BPI (Bidders Per Item) ‚Äî the human-behavior discovery engine\n\n---\n\n## Backlog (Prioritized)\n\n1. ~~DealFlow Admin~~ ‚úÖ\n2. ~~Nothing Machine MVP~~ ‚úÖ\n3. ~~Friend Invite Flow~~ ‚úÖ\n4. Seeding Infrastructure (needs $200K funding)\n5. **Referral Link System** ‚Üê NEXT TECHNICAL\n6. Timer System Fix\n7. Inspection System ($10K+ items)\n8. Garthbucks Ecosystem\n9. Community Governance\n10. Agentic Team Hiring\n\n---\n\n## North Star (Updated Feb 9)\n\n**1 Million Weekly Active Sellers**\n\n*Sellers bring the buyers. Supply creates demand. Focus on the source.*\n\n---\n\n*Last updated: February 9, 2026*\n",
