    id: 'product-roadmap-garth-algorithm',
    name: 'garth-algorithm.md',
    path: '/product-roadmap/garth-algorithm.md',
    type: 'knowledge',
    content: "Garth algorithm\r\n\r\nWhen you onboard we ask what sort of stuff your interested in\r\n\r\nThen instead of a lot % everything is assigned a \"Garth rating of 0 -> 99.9\r\n\r\nIf an item has a high Garth rating + fits your interest it's recommended to you\r\n\r\nSo we will have\r\n\r\nFeatured\r\nRecommended\r\nBrowse\r\n\r\nBrowse could be ranked simply by when item was posted + reposts filtered to the bottom\r\n\r\nThe Garth Rating is a weighted score based on sell % + reviews + gross value of seller combined with the desired price versus the price our data suggests!\r\n",
