    content: "we need to add this into richards reminder system its important!! 10 daily idea brainstorm monitored by richard.\r\n\r\n**HIGH-SIGNAL ‚Äî SHOULD GO INTO NOTION / BUILD PIPELINE**\r\n\r\n**1. Marketing Kill Shot:**\r\n\r\n**\"We convince you with math, not trust.\"**\r\n\r\nKEEP\r\n\r\n- Why it matters: This is a category-level positioning line. Instantly differentiates you from every auction house.\r\n- What to build:\r\n    - Homepage hero line\r\n    - Sales deck opener\r\n    - 5‚Äì10 sec cold open for ads\r\n    - Seller onboarding copy\r\n\r\nThis is foundational. Lock it.\r\n\r\n**2. Marketing Kill Shot:**\r\n\r\n**\"In the age of AI, we are the 100x auctioneer.\"**\r\n\r\nKEEP\r\n\r\n- Why it matters: Compresses leverage, scale, and inevitability into one sentence.\r\n- What to build:\r\n    - Pair with a visual: human auctioneer vs GarthAI\r\n    - Short explainer page: \"What does 100x mean?\"\r\n\r\n**5.**\r\n\r\n**Live Stream Authenticity / Proof-of-Liveness**\r\n\r\nKEEP (FUTURE CRITICAL)\r\n\r\n- Why it matters: This becomes huge once fake streams become common.\r\n- What to build (v1 concept):\r\n    - Cryptographic timestamp + rotating live challenge\r\n    - \"Say this phrase / show this object\" style proof\r\n    - Badge: \"Verified Live\"\r\n\r\nNot urgent, but very real moat later.\r\n",
