    content: "Video Recap\r\n\r\nA few times a week, build up a full story of the item.\r\n\r\nThe pictures, the video, the inspection, marketing. The bidding. etc.\r\n\r\nThis is a place future sellers who want to ponder selling with us can go watch what we do.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nSo I just had an idea about unreserved items over a certain value, maybe 25,050K, something... These items get a launch story. A full cinematic video that captures the item, the seller's story, why they're selling it, a little bit about the seller's life, just almost like a documentary about the item. \"launch story\" Since we are now making higher fees off items, we can justify this type of thing. I think it would be brilliant.\r\n",
