    path: '/reference/meaning-projects.md',
    type: 'knowledge',
    content: "# Meaning Projects\r\n\r\n**Allocation:** 10% of profit deployment.\r\n\r\nThese are **not businesses**. They are expressions of conviction and service. They exist because meaning is why the company operates.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Strict Rules (Non-Negotiable)\r\n\r\n- Fully legal\r\n- Transparent\r\n- Defensive, not violent\r\n- Partnership-based (NGOs, academics, institutions)\r\n- No private force, no vigilantism, no militias\r\n- If a project risks the company ‚Üí it is redesigned or shut down\r\n\r\n**Meaning must never destroy the platform that enables it.**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Projects\r\n\r\n### BibleAGI\r\n\r\nBringing the Bible to life with AI + historians in the loop, Wikipedia-style governance.\r\n\r\n**Approach:**\r\n- AI-powered exploration of scripture\r\n- Historian and scholar participation for accuracy\r\n- Community governance model (Wikipedia-style)\r\n- Educational, not doctrinal\r\n\r\n### The Armory\r\n\r\nTeaching young men about the Bible ‚Äî discipline, faith, responsibility.\r\n\r\n**Approach:**\r\n- Education, not combat\r\n- Character formation and mentorship\r\n- Structured programs rooted in biblical principles\r\n\r\n### Anti-Trafficking Support\r\n\r\nSupporting the fight against child trafficking in North America.\r\n\r\n**Approach:**\r\n- Funding research and technology\r\n- Survivor support programs\r\n- Lawful cooperation with authorities\r\n- Partnership with established NGOs and institutions\r\n- No private operations ‚Äî strictly support and funding\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Operating Principle\r\n\r\nIf legality or ethics are unclear on any meaning project ‚Üí it **pauses immediately**. These projects serve conviction. They must never create legal, ethical, or reputational risk for the platform.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Why These Exist\r\n\r\n> The Index is conviction. Operating cash is oxygen. Options are play. Land is survival. Revenue is fuel. **Meaning is why.**\r\n",
